snippet.title: Ultimate Rivals: The Rink - Gameplay Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
For the first time on NHL ice, star athletes from every sport including Alex Morgan, De'Aaron Fox, Jose Altuve, Justin Turner, Wayne Gretzky, Alex Ovechkin, Skylar Diggins-Smith, and JuJu Smith Schuster, face off in this total-crossover hockey showdown. As worlds converge, a new type of action arcade game arises, with rivalries and alliances never before imagined.

https://apple.co/-TheRink
